Ques 1: List at least 5 (five) data points that are required for the analysis and detection of a credit card fraud. (3 marks)

ANS: For the analysis and detection of credit card fraud, several data points can be helpful. below are 5 of them.
1. IP Address 
2. Shipping Address 
3. Transaction Date
4. Transaction value
5. Unites Purchase

